{"title":"Bike Parks in Paradise, Kona Presents the Maui Dream Build Sweepstakes","link":"https://bikerumor.com/bike-parks-in-paradise-kona-presents-the-maui-dream-build-sweepstakes/","date":1734120559000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-hero-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photos / Kona Bikes)\" /></p>\n<p>Want a chance to win a dream build Kona Process 134 CR DL and support a great cause? This special edition of Kona’s Dream Build Feature is called the <a href=\"https://go.rallyup.com/mauidreambuild/Campaign/Details\" target=\"_blank\">Maui Dream Buld Sweepstakes</a>. And its goal is to help raise funds needed to complete Maui’s own bike park.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-smokey-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-smokey-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Kona Maui Dream Build Sweepstakes smokey\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-smokey-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-smokey-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-smokey-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-smokey-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-smokey-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-smokey-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Kona Bikes)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The park is located a smidge North of Lahaina, Hi. After last year’s wildfires, the West Maui and Lahaina communities have pulled together with help from some friends on the mainland. They are working together to “create a space for all to ride, progress, and fall in love with this amazing location. Just like the pros that built the past did. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-bundle-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-bundle-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Kona Maui Dream Build Sweepstakes bundle\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-bundle-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-bundle-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-bundle-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-bundle-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-bundle-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-bundle-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Plus…gear from Troy Lee Designs, Maxxis, and Peak Designs.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-wolf-tooth-headset-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-wolf-tooth-headset-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Kona Maui Dream Build Sweepstakes wolf tooth headset\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-wolf-tooth-headset-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-wolf-tooth-headset-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-wolf-tooth-headset-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/up