pstakes-OneUp-bars-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-OneUp-bars-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-OneUp-bars-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-OneUp-bars-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-DT-Swiss-ft-hub-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-DT-Swiss-ft-hub-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Kona Maui Dream Build Sweepstakes DT Swiss ft hub\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-DT-Swiss-ft-hub-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-DT-Swiss-ft-hub-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-DT-Swiss-ft-hub-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-DT-Swiss-ft-hub-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-DT-Swiss-ft-hub-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-DT-Swiss-ft-hub-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The prize package is worth over a whopping $16,000 USD! Brands that have jumped on board to contribute to the cause are as follows:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.sram.com/en/sram/mountain\" target=\"_blank\">SRAM</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.sram.com/en/rockshox\" target=\"_blank\">RockShox</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.dtswiss.com/en/wheels/wheels-mtb\" target=\"_blank\">DT Swiss</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.oneupcomponents.com/\" target=\"_blank\">OneUp Components</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Wolf Tooth Components</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thesensus.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Sensus</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.peakdesign.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Peak Design</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>Plus assorted gear from <a href=\"https://troyleedesigns.com/collections/bike\" target=\"_blank\">Troy Lee Designs</a>, and an assortment of tires for all conditions, from <a href=\"https://www.maxxis.com/us/\" target=\"_blank\">Maxxis</a>. </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Enter To Win the Dream Build!</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-last-picture-jpeg.webp\"><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-last-picture-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Kona Maui Dream Build Sweepstakes last picture\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-last-picture-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-last-picture-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-last-picture-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-last-picture-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-last-picture-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Kona-Maui-Dream-Build-Sweepstakes-last-picture-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All of the money raised will go to the creation of a new public West Maui Bike Park through the <a href=\"https://www.mauimountainbike.org/napilibikepark\" target=\"_blank\">Maui Mountain Bike Coalition</a>. Both Cody Wilkins and Cam Zink from Sensus RAD Trails are building this park with the assistance of pros Carson Storch, Damon Iwanaga, Kyle Strait, and Kona’s own Eddie Reynolds. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can enter the Kona Maui Dream Build Sweepstakes <a href=\"https://go.rallyup.com/mauidreambuild/Campaign/Details\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a>! </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.konaworld.com/\" target=\"_blank\">KonaBikes.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bike-parks-in-paradise-kona-presents-the-maui-dream-build-sweepstakes/\">Bike Parks in Paradise, Kona Presents the Maui Dream Build Sweepstakes</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"e80ea1aecbe3c3016462d6bffafcdacdebb48e9a48bf226a275e373bad0f0ed9","category":"Cycling"}